title: Zac Efron, Dawn Wells, Chuck Berry: Oct. 18 celebrity birthdays
text:
The Associated Press
Published: Oct. 17, 2015 Updated: 10:48 p.m. If today is your birthday, have a slice of cake for one of these celebrities.�
Singer-guitarist Chuck Berry is 89.
Actress Dawn Wells (“Gilligan’s Island”) is 77.
Actor Joe Morton (“Scandal”) is 68.
Actress Pam Dawber is 65.
Actress Erin Moran is 55.
Actor Jean-Claude Van Damme is 55.
Jazz trumpeter Wynton Marsalis is 54.
Actor Vincent Spano is 53.
Actress Joy Bryant (“Parenthood”) is 41.
Guitarist Peter Svensson of the Cardigans is 41.
Actor Wesley Jonathan is 37.
Singer Ne-Yo is 36.
Country singer and “American Idol” contestant Josh Gracin is 35.
Jazz musician Esperanza Spalding is 31.
Actor Zac Efron is 28.
Actress Joy Lauren (“Desperate Housewives”) is 26.
Actor Tyler Posey is 24.

1927 George C. Scott , actor; died 1999.
